      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air, then boil a full kettle</p><p>Combine your <strong>chicken breast strips </strong>and<strong> ground cumin </strong>in a bowl with your <strong>dried oregano</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>coated chicken</strong></p>",
