            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, add the juice of the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime </strong>and cook for 1 min</p><p>Remove the pan from the heat and shred the chicken apart, using two forks – this is your <strong>Peruvian-style chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
